FORMAT: 1A
HOST: http://localhost:5000

# Library Management API

Demo API thư viện tối giản: chỉ gồm health và CRUD sách.

# Group Health

## Health Check [/health]

### Get service health [GET]

+ Response 200 (application/json)

        {
          "success": true,
          "message": "Service healthy",
          "data": {
            "status": "ok"
          }
        }

# Group Books

## Books Collection [/books]

### List books [GET]

+ Response 200 (application/json)

        {
          "success": true,
          "message": "Success",
          "data": [
            {
              "id": 1,
              "title": "Clean Code",
              "author": "Robert C. Martin"
            }
          ]
        }

### Create book [POST]

+ Request (application/json)

        {
          "title": "Domain-Driven Design",
          "author": "Eric Evans"
        }

+ Response 201 (application/json)

        {
          "success": true,
          "message": "Book created",
          "data": {
            "id": 2,
            "title": "Domain-Driven Design",
            "author": "Eric Evans"
          }
        }

## Book Detail [/books/{bookId}]

+ Parameters
    + bookId: `1` (number, required)

### Get book by id [GET]

+ Response 200 (application/json)

        {
          "success": true,
          "message": "Success",
          "data": {
            "id": 1,
            "title": "Clean Code",
            "author": "Robert C. Martin"
          }
        }

+ Response 404 (application/json)

        {
          "success": false,
          "error": "Book not found"
        }

### Update book [PUT]

+ Request (application/json)

        {
          "title": "Clean Code 2nd Edition",
          "author": "Robert C. Martin"
        }

+ Response 200 (application/json)

        {
          "success": true,
          "message": "Book updated",
          "data": {
            "id": 1,
            "title": "Clean Code 2nd Edition",
            "author": "Robert C. Martin"
          }
        }

### Delete book [DELETE]

+ Response 200 (application/json)

        {
          "success": true,
          "message": "Book deleted",
          "data": null
        }
